Subject: File server migration
Description:
Hi Support

This is relates to ticket# 00370902 that a logged some time back.

Im following up if anyhing has changed relating to the feature request you suggested.

Also do you have any other customers that has done a migration from one file server to another file server and retaining the activity data and can  you possibly assist with a solution.

Regards
Warren
What_We_Know__c: Wants to migrate everything collected/configured since they are changing from netapp to WFS
Next_Steps__c: Check around but its unlikely to happen
Solution_Comment__c:
The data can not be safely migrated between two distinct collectors and should be rescanned instead.
Also answered some questions.
Not sending a resolution template to avoid aggravating the customer, due to the amount of work they need to do for re-adding the entire FS.
